            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="tougao-user">感謝 IT 之家網友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1168596" rel="nofollow">手可摘星辰</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D284961" rel="nofollow">Hassy</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1478139" rel="nofollow">ThreeDrops_Water</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1267235" rel="nofollow">去繁就簡</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1234925" rel="nofollow">墨笙</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D931763" rel="nofollow">陳雨晨</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1860885" rel="nofollow">青衫磊落 zck</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1119148" rel="nofollow">jingyu_</a> 的線索投遞！</div><p data-vmark="93b2">13:52 更新：喜馬拉雅官方微博表示，<span class="accentTextColor">目前已緊急修復，不會影響大家的會員等權益</span>。</p><p data-vmark="ccc3" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/aeae7ff8-26db-4392-b68f-8d6f339f7edd.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="785" h="265" title="（更新：已修復）「喜馬拉雅崩了」登上熱搜，網友誤以為是「山崩了」" width="785" height="265" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="c031"><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT 之家</a> 12 月 19 日消息，據多位 IT 之家小夥伴投稿，喜馬拉雅 App 出現服務問題，<span class="accentTextColor">在有會員的情況下依然提示購買才能播放</span>，還會出現 502 錯誤。</p><p data-vmark="fdd8" style="text-align: center;"><span class="post-img-item"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/fb5fe638-e1c7-494e-8603-7f177b1b7a63.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE1OS5wbmc=,t_100,g_3,y_16,x_16,a_0/format,f_auto" title="（更新：已修復）「喜馬拉雅崩了」登上熱搜，網友誤以為是「山崩了」" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span></p><p data-vmark="f8aa" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/05422a42-ffc8-4b05-828b-f2a609a9eeb3.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzg5LnBuZw==,t_100,g_6,y_10,x_9,a_0/format,f_auto" w="576" h="1186" title="（更新：已修復）「喜馬拉雅崩了」登上熱搜，網友誤以為是「山崩了」" width="576" height="1186" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="4446" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="post-img-item"></span>截至 IT 之家發稿，<span class="accentTextColor">「喜馬拉雅崩了」已排名微博熱搜第二</span>，然而不少網友表示是被「騙進來」的，誤以為是地震導致「喜馬拉雅山崩了」。</p><p data-vmark="fade" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/359368a5-fd73-46fc-a3e0-ce9323f7e3d3.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="351" h="96" title="（更新：已修復）「喜馬拉雅崩了」登上熱搜，網友誤以為是「山崩了」" width="351" height="96" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="b0b8" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/5fb1d28f-836d-4049-a90a-bf47448df740.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="809" h="955" title="（更新：已修復）「喜馬拉雅崩了」登上熱搜，網友誤以為是「山崩了」" width="809" height="955" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="a59c">喜馬拉雅是一家音頻分享平台，彙集了有聲小説、兒童故事、相聲評書、京劇戲曲、新聞段子、廣播電台等音頻內容。</p><p class="ad-tips">廣告聲明：文內含有的對外跳轉鏈接（包括不限於超鏈接、二維碼、口令等形式），用於傳遞更多信息，節省甄選時間，結果僅供參考，IT 之家所有文章均包含本聲明。</p>
